          "value": ""
        },
        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "The only way to get to the Skinlands is through a Null.  Right now, I've made Nulls big bright and shiny (see the one behind this sign).  Other GMs may make them invisible, or denote them with some other effect.  Null's represent weak spots in the barrier between the Shadowlands and the Skinlands.  At night, the barrier is weak enough that Wraiths can pass through.  It is impossible during the day.  "
          }
        }
      },
      {
