        },
        "Speaker": {
          "type": "cexostring",
          "value": ""
        },
        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "Based on your current level, you will have two powers, Cross Over and Poltergeist.  Cross Over allows you to manifest in some way, like, a ghostly image.  The stronger your ability, the more you can Cross Over.  All Wraiths can speak to the living.  The next stage of Cross Over is appearing (but being unable to touch), the appearing and being able to touch a little bit, and finally, the most powerful Wraiths can Cross Over enough to effectively be human throughout the night, although, this always fades at dawn.  Poltergeist is the ability to create strange effects in the Real World.  Blinking lights, torches that go out, candles that suddenly light, mysterious blood stains that fade over time, fog, ice, images of tortured souls, etc.  The most powerful Poltergeists can actually summon a swarm of vermin to torment the living.    "
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "__struct_id": 5,
        "Animation": {
          "type": "dword",
          "value": 0
        },
        "AnimLoop": {
          "type": "byte",
          "value": 1
        },
